{
  "stem": "9168.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second experiment was freezing or hypothermia, which was the experiment to which, over the many years, doctors in other parts of the world tried to look to find some-- something good that came out of this experiment.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hypothermia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think, for the most part, failed to find the merit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I always thought it would have been very unethical anyway to even search, because of the methods used.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this-- this experiment, freezing was conducted from 1942 to 1943, which was my first year in college.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought about that when the years came out in the testimony.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "To determine the most effective means of heating severely chilled or frozen people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The victims-- I remember the photographs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were placed in long, narrow tanks of ice water, and I can still see them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For up to three hours, at which point, death occurred, or by keeping them outdoors naked from 9 to 14 hours in sub-freezing temperatures.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the testimony that they screamed in pain as parts of their bodies froze.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then the rewarming of those who did not die was most effective by very hot baths.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then Heinrich Himmler, who was the chief of the Gestapo, a major Nazi leader who committed suicide after he was captured by the British, ordered rewarming by naked women.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I guess this was, maybe, one of the first truly shocking bits of testimony that I certainly heard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at one point, four gypsy prostitutes, themselves prisoners, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were produced from Ravensbruck concentration camp to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the chilled-to-unconsciousness male-- male, naked victim was placed between the two naked women, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just indicating how obscene all of this was.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
